room_title: Escape room "Nightmare on High Street" by Adventures of Escaping in Millville
room_description: Welcome to the town of Springwood, where things are gettin' creepy! You and your friends are in the bedroom of Freddy’s next victims... and he’s wanting all of you. Can you and your crew save yourselves and become the heroes of this tiny town? Solve Freddy’s twisted tests to save the town and children of Springwood!
